<div class="block mx-auto my-12 p-8 bg-white w-1/3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-lg text-gray-800"
    style="margin-top: 140px;">

    <p>Bienvenido a la zona de clientes.</p>
    <p>Desde aquí podrás realizar reservas, ver el estado de tus bonos, ver tus reservas, editar tus datos, etc..</p>
    <br>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Login</h1>

    <form action="" method="post" class="mt-4">

        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email"
            class="border border-gray-200 w-full text-lg placeholder-gray-500 p-2 my-2 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white"
            required>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Contraseña"
            class="border border-gray-200 w-full text-lg placeholder-gray-500 p-2 my-2 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white"
            required>
        <button type="submit"
            class="rounded-md bg-green-500 w-full text-lg text-white font-semibold p-2 my-3 hover:bg-green-600 focus:bg-green-700">Iniciar
            sesión</button>
        <button type="reset"
            class="rounded-md bg-green-500 w-full text-lg text-white font-semibold p-2 my-3 hover:bg-green-600 focus:bg-green-700">Limpiar</button>

        {{#if error}}
        <p class="text-red-500 font-bold text-lg my-3">*{{error}}</p>
        {{/if}}
    </form>

</div>